: null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Cover-Landscape_2560x1440px.png", "id": "802213135371789", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982672_802213138705122_4667017097399142221_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=bV5h-DsxxyQQ7kNvgHI-XWN&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCIguTO9N51ZkiADoeUeHryJFwP3juvVDSYt2ZPbPh6bg&oe=66CC8536"}, "display_name": "Simulador Soft Skills", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Transform your potential and excel in your career!\nDiscover the simulator designed to enhance your \"Soft Skills\" through 5 essential training capsules with which you will be able to: \n\n1\ufe0f\u20e3 Self-assess your transversal competencies that will help you adapt to different work environments.\n2\ufe0f\u20e3 Defend a speech in front of an audience to improve your communication and public speaking skills.\n3\ufe0f\u20e3 Train your strengths in a commercial speech.\n4\ufe0f\u20e3 Make decisions to develop your strategic and analytical skills.\n5\ufe0f\u20e3 Work as part of a team to foster collaboration and group efficiency.", "short_description": "Boost your \"Soft Skills\" with our Virtual Reality Simulator! \n\nComposed of 5 training capsules to: \n1\ufe0f\u20e3 Self-assess your transversal competences.\n2\ufe0f\u20e3 Improve your communication and public speaking skills.\n3\ufe0f\u20e3 Defend a commercial speech.\n4\ufe0f\u20e3 Speed up decision making.\n5\ufe0f\u20e3 Promote teamwork.\n\nIdeal for professionals looking to improve their interpersonal skills in an immersive, interactive and effective way!"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "SoftSkills_Logo_8100x1296px.png", "id": "1158856758691457", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974786_1158856762024790_8351105602424236604_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=WdbEKV9hgs4Q7kNvgGKL7lu&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBb9nabY-KcZ7x2AS-CpcATS_W9Hz7VSfbo5H32xOwlkQ&oe=6